{"tid":1940520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國戲院開始復工　單日票房僅3萬元","createTime":"2020-03-23T22:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T03:06:38.000Z","uid":41343,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9268086ef0c86b23a4449653d8a8044d38b9f0d4","tid":1940520,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T22:56:02.000Z","msg":"肺炎蔓延全球，全球多個地區正大規模爆發，不過中國的情況似乎有所緩和。據中國媒體報道，中國各行業都正在陸續復工，而在新春期間受到最大打擊的電影院，亦在本月20日開始復工，復工率為4.47%。<br />\n<br />\n中國購票平台、同時記錄票房的公司「貓眼電影」，由1月24日起停止統計票房。不過截至昨日（21日）有507間電影院復工，又重新開始發布記錄，而昨日單日的票房記錄約3萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n不過，現時上映的電影並非新電影，例如《戰狼2》、《流浪地球》等，而未上映的新電影則暫時未有新消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2597396/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E5%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%80%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF%E5%83%853%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2597396%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%25B2%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A7%258B%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%2583%25853%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1qCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=8fa9c3ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2597396/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E5%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%80%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF%E5%83%853%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83</a>"},{"pid":"50ddcdaafbdd1b480bf0e68c75d4cbf8cd312300","tid":1940520,"uid":47674,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T23:44:15.000Z","msg":"3萬，thanks!"},{"pid":"f9422f01afc233d90c01a98a57bb37ae98812067","tid":1940520,"uid":170249,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T23:46:19.000Z","msg":"連支那小粉